	<a href="http://holocaustcentre.com/Museum">Museum & Memorial</a></div><div class="nav_menu_link nav_L1" >
	<a href="http://holocaustcentre.com/Museum/Bronze-Doors">Bronze Doors</a></div><div class="nav_menu_link nav_L1" >
	<a href="http://holocaustcentre.com/Museum/Hall-of-Memories">Hall of Memories</a></div></div>

</div></div>
