    <section class="column one">
		<h1>Holocaust Museum and Memorial</h1>
		<div id="body_content"><div class="" >
			<div class="small_paragraph" style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; color: #474444; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;">
<p>The Neuberger houses a permanent collection of archival photographs, art, artefacts and testimony. Our current museum exhibit,&nbsp;<em style="font-style: italic;">Young Voices from the Holocaust,</em>&nbsp;features several collection highlights.</p>
<p>Our interactive portrait gallery entitled,&nbsp;<em style="font-style: italic;">We Who Survived,</em>&nbsp;is a photographic tribute to the members of our survivor speakers' bureau.&nbsp;</p>
<p>The gateway to the museum is a set of iconographic bronze doors created by sculptor Andrew Posa.</p>
<p>The Hall of Memories, the memorial inside the museum, is a place of remembrance and reflection for visitors.</p>
</div>
		</div><div class="" >
			<h3 class="paragraph_subtitle">Visiting the Museum</h3>
		</div><div class="" >
			<p>The Neuberger Holocaust Education Centre is pleased to welcome you to our museum and create a visitor experience tailored to your group's needs.</p>
<p>For museum information, including address and directions, <a title="Visit" href="http://holocaustcentre.com/About/Visit" rel="78">click here</a>.</p>
<p>For information about booking a group visit, <a title="Field Trip" href="http://holocaustcentre.com/Educators-Students/Field-Trip" rel="64">click here</a>.</p>
<p>For general inquiries, please call 416.631.5689.</p>
<p><strong>Regrettably, due to regularly scheduled tours and space restrictions, walk-ins cannot always be accommodated.&nbsp;<em>We strongly encourage calling in advance of your visit.</em></strong></p>
<p><strong>If a museum visit is cancelled with less than two weeks notice, an administrative fee of $50 will be charged.&nbsp;</strong></p>
		</div></div>
	</section>

	<section class="column one right right_sidebar last">
